giant babies with Becky.

15:25.670 --> 15:27.830
I...

15:27.830 --> 15:31.960
I want tiny, psychotic babies
with you.

15:31.960 --> 15:33.710
[ Lock clicks ]

15:37.120 --> 15:38.880
[ Sighs ]

15:38.880 --> 15:40.710
Tell me what's going on,
Darlene.

15:42.120 --> 15:43.670
I get why
you're attracted to her.

15:43.670 --> 15:45.120
[ Laughing ] What?!

15:45.120 --> 15:47.500
