to have a family.

15:51.830 --> 15:53.620
Yeah,
I want to have a family.

15:53.620 --> 15:54.830
With you.

15:54.830 --> 15:56.170
Well, maybe I can't.

15:56.170 --> 15:57.540
[ Scoffs ]

15:57.540 --> 16:01.210
Look, we haven't even been
trying that long!

16:01.210 --> 16:03.000
