gotta be positive.

16:03.000 --> 16:06.000
Oh, fine. I'll just change
my entire personality.

16:08.620 --> 16:09.920
Oh, look at that.

16:09.920 --> 16:12.710
The sun'll come out tomorrow,
and, bam, I'm pregnant!

16:12.710 --> 16:14.580
[ Scoffs ]

16:14.580 --> 16:16.460
[ Sighs ]

16:16.460 --> 16:18.210
Did something happen
at the doctor?

16:19.540 --> 16:22.420
