upside down from the ceiling,

17:57.080 --> 17:59.420
like a bat,
to increase our chances.

18:01.500 --> 18:04.000
You just want the change
that'll fall out of my pockets.

18:05.750 --> 18:08.330
Well, I assumed you'd be naked
at that point, but whatever.

18:11.620 --> 18:13.120
Mm.

18:13.120 --> 18:16.670
