my emotional baggage on Becky.

18:16.670 --> 18:19.170
[ Scoffs ] How do you think
I feel as her new husband?

18:20.790 --> 18:22.880
♪♪

18:22.880 --> 18:26.420
[ Indistinct talking
on television ]

18:26.420 --> 18:28.460
I can take that bear.

18:30.170 --> 18:32.250
[ Knock on door ]

18:34.290 --> 18:35.330
[ TV shuts off ]

18:35.330 --> 18:36.460
[ Knock on door ]

18:36.460 --> 18:38.000
If you're drunk,
this isn't your house!

18:41.040 --> 18:42.460
