is wrong with you?!

18:42.460 --> 18:44.710
You see me kissing a guy,

18:44.710 --> 18:47.460
and that's who you use
to tell me you love me?

18:47.460 --> 18:51.960
I can see why you like him.
He's real easy to talk to.

18:51.960 --> 18:54.420
This is so high school.

18:54.420 --> 18:56.460
You might as well
pass me a note saying

18:56.460 --> 18:58.710
"Do you like Dan?
Check yes or no."

18:58.710 --> 19:00.830
Well, the last time
I did anything like this,

19:00.830 --> 19:01.960
I was in high school!

19:01.960 --> 19:03.580
Well, you're a man now.

19:03.580 --> 19:06.000
And I just drove
212 miles.

19:06.000 --> 19:07.460
Tell me to my face!

19:08.670 --> 19:09.790
I love you.

19:11.040 --> 19:13.500
