if I tell you to say it.

19:14.880 --> 19:16.120
I don't know
how to do this.

19:16.120 --> 19:17.880
I'm no good
at any of this stuff.

19:17.880 --> 19:19.830
I'm no good
at expressing myself.

19:19.830 --> 19:22.000
[ Groans ]

19:22.000 --> 19:24.290
