19:44.670 --> 19:46.620
Well...

19:46.620 --> 19:48.960
you know, um...

19:48.960 --> 19:51.460
with that ring off,

19:51.460 --> 19:54.620
lots of women
are gonna be coming after ya.

19:54.620 --> 19:56.330
Including you?

19:56.330 --> 19:58.290
Well...

19:58.290 --> 19:59.330
maybe.

20:00.790 --> 20:03.500
You had your chance.

20:03.500 --> 20:06.710
I would like to see
what else is out there.

20:06.710 --> 20:08.080
[ Scoffs ]

20:08.080 --> 20:10.420
Have you been to
a high school reunion lately?

20:14.750 --> 20:17.080
