20:49.120 --> 20:52.790
Hey, your doctor told you
you couldn't have a baby,

20:52.790 --> 20:54.380
and he was wrong.

20:54.380 --> 20:55.880
I mean, they make mistakes
all the time, right?

20:55.880 --> 20:57.290
Of course!

20:57.290 --> 20:58.830
All the time!

20:58.830 --> 21:01.790
Besides, having another baby
is gonna ruin your life,

21:01.790 --> 21:03.500
