and have sex with Emilio.

21:16.620 --> 21:17.710
Well, you heard her.

21:17.710 --> 21:19.210
If we're serious
about the baby,

21:19.210 --> 21:20.830
you have to go have sex
with Emilio.

21:20.830 --> 21:22.420
Hey, he's smokin' hot.

21:22.420 --> 21:23.960
